Class GenericElementResource<T extends Atom>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.system.rest.resources.GenericElementResource<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
GenericSetResource, PluginRunResource, ReferenceResource, TagResource, UserResource
public abstract class GenericElementResource<T extends Atom>
extends Object

Describes the basic operations that we wish to define on elements (which may or may not be found inside sets).

dyuen
